desc:
The default Provider implementation which saves state via cookies.
<br />Usage:
 <pre><code>
   var cp = new Roo.state.CookieProvider({
       path: "/cgi-bin/",
       expires: new Date(new Date().getTime()+(1000*60*60*24*30)); //30 days
       domain: "roojs.com"
   })
   Roo.state.Manager.setProvider(cp);
 </code></pre>
